data.mission: Produce the 12-page roadmap and project-management package: near-term (6–12 months) and medium-term (1–3 years) prioritized research projects, recommended collaborations (including specific analogue labs and experimental groups), compute and data requirements, milestones for paper submissions, datasets, prototyping workshops, and assigned roles (writing leads, technical leads, editorial coordinator, QA). Create a timeline and milestone tracker suitable for use in team coordination.
Evaluate task artifacts against acceptance criteria
